<br>
The answer to your question depends on if you are trying to solo, or group. Or how important cash is to you. If it were me, leveling my paladin over again, I would be going to Kurns tower in FoB.. I would get a bind in Kaesora, and grind in Kurns. Lots of undead, the ideal mob for paladins to hunt. It would take you to 18 ish, then you have some choices to make. I would make this decision if you dont want to earn money since there is no where to bank for a paladin there.<br>
<br>
Once 17-18 you can start the LoIO/FM/OT/DL grind, but since I abhorr those people, I am going to recommend against it.<br>
<br>
Go the Highpass/Highkeep basement/Dalnir/ Lower Guk route. That is the current program I am taking with my war, and it is serving me well. <p>
